revision.text: measurement unit label Examples of measurement unit labels are liters, inches, weight per volume. A data item label that denotes a unit of measure. Une étiquette de donnée qui dénote une unité de mesure. 2009-03-16: review of this term done during during the OBI workshop winter 2009 and the current definition was considered acceptable for use in OBI. If there is a need to modify this definition please notify OBI. Jean-Marc Meunier PERSON: Alan Ruttenberg PERSON: Melanie Courtot is a subclass from data item label
